<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>小红书账号分析报告</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --canvas: #F7F6F3;
      --surface: #FFFFFF;
      --surface-soft: #F9F9F8;
      --ink: #2F3437;
      --ink-strong: #111111;
      --muted: #787774;
      --line: #EAEAEA;
      --line-soft: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      --blue-bg: #E1F3FE;
      --blue-text: #1F6C9F;
      --green-bg: #EDF3EC;
      --green-text: #346538;
      --yellow-bg: #FBF3DB;
      --yellow-text: #956400;
      --red-bg: #FDEBEC;
      --red-text: #9F2F2D;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--canvas);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: 'SF Pro Display', 'Geist Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Switzer', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0.18;
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
      width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    .report-shell {
      width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 0 72px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 14px 0 32px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      color: var(--ink-strong);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      border: 2px solid var(--ink-strong);
      border-radius: 4px;
      display: inline-block;
      position: relative;
    }

    .brand-mark::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      right: 3px;
      bottom: 3px;
      background: var(--ink-strong);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .toc {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .toc a {
      border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .toc a:hover { border-color: var(--ink-strong); }

    .hero {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: clamp(32px, 6vw, 72px);
      min-height: 420px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.35fr) minmax(280px, 0.65fr);
      gap: 48px;
      align-items: end;
    }

    .eyebrow,
    .tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      width: fit-content;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      background: var(--yellow-bg);
      color: var(--yellow-text);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    h1,
    .display {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--ink-strong);
      font-family: 'Lyon Text', 'Newsreader', 'Playfair Display', 'Instrument Serif', serif;
      font-size: 72px;
      line-height: 0.96;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      max-width: 880px;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      margin: 24px 0 0;
      max-width: 680px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .metric-stack {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .metric-card,
    .card,
    .section-panel,
    .finding-card,
    .table-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .metric-card {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .metric-label,
    .meta-label {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }

    .metric-value {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: var(--ink-strong);
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 760;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    section {
      padding: 72px 0 0;
    }

    .section-heading {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    h2 {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--ink-strong);
      font-size: 42px;
      line-height: 1.08;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .section-kicker {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .section-lede {
      margin: 14px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 17px;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .bento {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .card,
    .finding-card {
      padding: 28px;
      transition: transform 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease;
    }

    .card:hover,
    .finding-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    }

    .span-7 { grid-column: span 7; }
    .span-5 { grid-column: span 5; }
    .span-4 { grid-column: span 4; }
    .span-6 { grid-column: span 6; }
    .span-12 { grid-column: span 12; }

    .card h3,
    .finding-card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--ink-strong);
      font-size: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .card p,
    .finding-card p {
      margin: 14px 0 0;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .tag.medium,
    .tag.strong { background: var(--green-bg); color: var(--green-text); }
    .tag.weak { background: var(--yellow-bg); color: var(--yellow-text); }
    .tag.not_judgable { background: var(--red-bg); color: var(--red-text); }
    .tag.info { background: var(--blue-bg); color: var(--blue-text); }

    .action-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .action-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 42px minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 24px;
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--surface);
    }

    .action-item h3 {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      color: var(--ink-strong);
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .action-meta-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .action-cell {
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px;
      background: var(--surface-soft);
    }

    .action-cell span {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .action-cell p {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .step-number {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: var(--ink-strong);
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: var(--surface-soft);
    }

    .section-panel {
      padding: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .panel-header {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 28px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      background: var(--surface-soft);
    }

    .panel-header h3 {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--ink-strong);
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .panel-header p {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .panel-body {
      padding: 28px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .finding-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .chart {
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 28px;
      background: var(--surface);
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .chart-badge { align-self: start; }
    .chart-multiples {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .chart-svg { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; overflow: visible; }
    .chart-svg text {
      font-family: 'SF Pro Display', 'Geist Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      fill: var(--ink);
    }
    .chart-svg .ca-title,
    .chart-svg .ca-cat { fill: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    .chart-svg .ca-num {
      fill: var(--ink-strong);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }
    .chart-svg .ca-empty { fill: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }
    .chart-svg .ca-axis,
    .chart-svg .ca-grid { stroke: var(--line); stroke-width: 1; }
    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .chart-multiples { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    @media print {
      .chart, .chart-svg {
        print-color-adjust: exact;
        -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      }
    }

    .result-block {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 0 0 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
    }

    .result-block:last-child {
      border-bottom: 0;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    .result-heading {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .result-heading h4 {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--ink-strong);
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .notice {
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px;
      background: var(--yellow-bg);
      color: var(--yellow-text);
    }

    .notice strong {
      color: var(--yellow-text);
    }

    .finding-card {
      background: var(--surface);
    }

    .finding-meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .numbers {
      margin: 18px 0 0;
      padding: 16px;
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--surface-soft);
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .number-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .field-name {
      display: grid;
      gap: 4px;
      font-family: 'SF Pro Display', 'Geist Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Switzer', sans-serif;
    }

    .field-name strong {
      color: var(--ink-strong);
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .field-name code,
    .field-code {
      width: fit-content;
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: var(--canvas);
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2px 5px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .field-help {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      font-weight: 400;
      max-width: 220px;
    }

    .note-list {
      margin: 16px 0 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .note-list li + li { margin-top: 6px; }

    details {
      border-top: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      padding: 0;
    }

    details:first-child { border-top: 0; }

    summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      list-style: none;
      padding: 18px 0;
      color: var(--ink-strong);
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }

    summary::after {
      content: "+";
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    details[open] summary::after { content: "-"; }

    .table-details {
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0 16px;
      background: var(--surface);
    }

    .table-details + .table-details {
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .summary-meta {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 4px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .table-caption {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .technical-details {
      border-top: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .technical-details summary {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .table-wrap {
      width: 100%;
      overflow-x: auto;
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      min-width: 680px;
      background: var(--surface);
    }

    th,
    td {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      text-align: left;
      vertical-align: top;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    th {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: var(--surface-soft);
    }

    td code,
    kbd {
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      background: var(--canvas);
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2px 5px;
    }

    .appendix-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .codex-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .codex-list li {
      padding: 16px;
      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--surface);
      font-weight: 650;
      color: var(--ink-strong);
    }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(12px);
      animation: enter 600ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
      animation-delay: calc(var(--index, 0) * 80ms);
    }

    @keyframes enter {
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .reveal {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: none;
        animation: none;
      }
      .card,
      .finding-card { transition: none; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .report-shell { width: min(100% - 24px, 1180px); }
      .topbar { align-items: flex-start; flex-direction: column; }
      .toc { justify-content: flex-start; }
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; padding: 32px; }
      h1 { font-size: 46px; line-height: 1.02; }
      h2 { font-size: 32px; line-height: 1.12; }
      .action-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .action-meta-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .bento,
      .finding-grid,
      .appendix-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .span-7,
      .span-5,
      .span-4,
      .span-6,
      .span-12 { grid-column: auto; }
      .panel-header { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="report-shell">
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="brand"><span class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true"></span> 小红书经营分析</div>
      <nav class="toc" aria-label="报告目录">
        <a href="#guide">经营导读</a>
        <a href="#actions">行动计划</a>
        <a href="#analysis">详细分析</a>
        <a href="#appendix">数据附录</a>
        <a href="#codex">Codex 追问</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero reveal" style="--index: 0">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Operating Report</span>
        <h1>小红书账号分析报告</h1>
        <p class="hero-copy">
          这份报告按经营问题组织：先看结论和下周动作，再看商品、内容、用户需求、实验和数据可信度。技术字段会保留在追溯区，不影响正常阅读。
        </p>
      </div>
      <aside class="metric-stack" aria-label="报告概览">
        <div class="metric-card">
          <span class="metric-label">分析模块</span>
          <span class="metric-value">{{ report.task_count }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-card">
          <span class="metric-label">经营发现</span>
          <span class="metric-value">{{ report.finding_count }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-card">
          <span class="metric-label">明细数据行</span>
          <span class="metric-value">{{ report.total_table_rows }}</span>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section id="guide" class="reveal" style="--index: 1">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="section-kicker">Reader Path</p>
        <h2>经营导读</h2>
        <p class="section-lede">
          先读这里就能知道本周最值得做什么。数据质量和原始字段放在后面，避免一打开报告就被机器字段打断。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bento">
        {% for item in report.highlights %}
        <article class="card {% if loop.first %}span-7{% else %}span-5{% endif %}">
          <span class="tag {{ item.evidence_class }}">可信度 {{ item.evidence }}</span>
          <h3>{{ item.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ item.body }}</p>
          <p class="meta-label">{{ item.help }}</p>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
        <article class="card span-12">
          <span class="tag info">How to read</span>
          <h3>这份报告怎么读</h3>
          <p>可信度说明这条结论适合怎么用：直接决策、短期观察、转成实验，或先补数据。</p>
          {% if report.evidence_chart_svg %}
          <div class="chart">{{ report.evidence_chart_svg }}</div>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="action-meta-grid">
            {% for item in report.evidence_counts %}
            <div class="action-cell">
              <span>
                {% if item.value == "not_judgable" %}
                不可判断
                {% else %}
                {{ item.label }}可信度
                {% endif %}
              </span>
              <p>{{ item.help }}</p>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="actions" class="reveal" style="--index: 2">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="section-kicker">Next Week</p>
        <h2>下周行动计划</h2>
        <p class="section-lede">
          每条行动都写清楚目标、原因、执行方式、观察指标和暂停条件。执行时一次只改一个变量，避免看不出到底是什么起作用。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="action-list">
        {% for action in report.actions %}
        <article class="action-item">
          <div class="step-number">{{ loop.index }}</div>
          <div>
            <span class="tag {{ action.evidence_class }}">可信度 {{ action.evidence }}</span>
            <h3>{{ action.task }}：{{ action.target }}</h3>
            <div class="action-meta-grid">
              <div class="action-cell">
                <span>为什么做</span>
                <p>{{ action.why }}</p>
              </div>
              <div class="action-cell">
                <span>怎么执行</span>
                <p>{{ action.how }}</p>
              </div>
              <div class="action-cell">
                <span>看什么指标</span>
                <p>{{ action.metric }}</p>
              </div>
              <div class="action-cell">
                <span>什么时候暂停</span>
                <p>{{ action.stop_rule }}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="analysis" class="reveal" style="--index: 3">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="section-kicker">Deep Dive</p>
        <h2>详细分析</h2>
        <p class="section-lede">
          这里按业务问题分组，不按程序模块排序。每个小节先讲结论，再给用户视图表格；需要查原始字段时，再展开技术追溯信息。
        </p>
      </div>

      {% for group in report.analysis_groups %}
      <article class="section-panel">
        <header class="panel-header">
          <div>
            <p class="section-kicker">Business Question</p>
            <h3>{{ group.title }}</h3>
            <p>{{ group.description }}</p>
          </div>
        </header>
        <div class="panel-body">
          {% for result in group.results %}
          <section class="result-block">
            <div class="result-heading">
              <span class="tag info">{{ result.label }}</span>
              <h4>{{ result.title }}</h4>
            </div>

            {% if result.limitations %}
            <div class="notice">
              <strong>数据限制</strong>
              <ul class="note-list">
                {% for limitation in result.limitations %}
                <li>{{ limitation }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
              </ul>
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if result.findings %}
            <div class="finding-grid">
              {% for finding in result.findings %}
              <article class="finding-card">
                <span class="tag {{ finding.evidence_class }}">可信度 {{ finding.evidence }}</span>
                <h3>{{ finding.title }}</h3>
                <p>{{ finding.body }}</p>

                {% if finding.evidence_reason %}
                <p><strong>可信度原因：</strong>{{ finding.evidence_reason }}</p>
                {% endif %}

                {% if finding.key_numbers %}
                <div class="numbers">
                  {% for item in finding.key_numbers %}
                  <div class="number-row">
                    <span class="field-name">
                      <strong>{{ item.label }}</strong>
                      <span class="field-help">{{ item.help }}</span>
                    </span>
                    <strong>{{ item.value }}</strong>
                  </div>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if finding.caveats %}
                <ul class="note-list">
                  {% for caveat in finding.caveats %}
                  <li>{{ caveat }}</li>
                  {% endfor %}
                </ul>
                {% endif %}

                {% if finding.recommended_action %}
                <p><strong>建议：</strong>{{ finding.recommended_action }}</p>
                {% endif %}
              </article>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% for table in result.table_views %}
            <details class="table-details">
              <summary>
                <span>
                  {{ table.label }}
                  <span class="summary-meta">用户视图：{{ table.display_text }}</span>
                </span>
              </summary>
              {% if table.row_count %}
              <p class="table-caption">
                用户视图只展示最适合经营判断的字段；完整字段和原始字段名在下方“技术追溯信息”里。
              </p>
              <div class="table-wrap">
                <table>
                  <thead>
                    <tr>
                      {% for column in table.user_columns %}
                      <th>
                        <span class="field-name">
                          <strong>{{ column.label }}</strong>
                          <span class="field-help">{{ column.help }}</span>
                        </span>
                      </th>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    {% for row in table.user_rows %}
                    <tr>
                      {% for cell in row %}
                      <td>{{ cell.value }}</td>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
              <details class="technical-details">
                <summary>技术追溯信息</summary>
                <p class="table-caption">
                  这里保留完整字段名，方便复查数据来源或继续让 Codex 做二次分析。
                </p>
                <div class="table-wrap">
                  <table>
                    <thead>
                      <tr>
                        {% for column in table.technical_columns %}
                        <th>
                          <span class="field-name">
                            <strong>{{ column.label }}</strong>
                            <code>{{ column.name }}</code>
                            <span class="field-help">{{ column.help }}</span>
                          </span>
                        </th>
                        {% endfor %}
                      </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                      {% for row in table.technical_rows %}
                      <tr>
                        {% for cell in row %}
                        <td>{{ cell.value }}</td>
                        {% endfor %}
                      </tr>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </div>
              </details>
              {% else %}
              <p class="section-lede">这个模块没有可展示的明细行。</p>
              {% endif %}
            </details>
            {% endfor %}
          </section>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </section>

    <section id="appendix" class="reveal" style="--index: 4">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="section-kicker">Appendix</p>
        <h2>数据附录</h2>
        <p class="section-lede">
          附录保留字段和机器表名，方便复查。普通读者可以只看中文解释；需要查数时再展开表格。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="appendix-grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>可信度说明</h3>
          {% for evidence in report.evidence_counts %}
          <div class="numbers">
            <div class="number-row"><span>{{ evidence.label }}</span><strong>{{ evidence.count }} 条</strong></div>
            <p>{{ evidence.help }}</p>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>术语解释</h3>
          {% for item in report.glossary %}
          <div class="numbers">
            <div class="number-row"><span>{{ item.term }}</span></div>
            <p>{{ item.definition }}</p>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="codex" class="reveal" style="--index: 5">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="section-kicker">Assistant Questions</p>
        <h2>可以问 Codex 的问题</h2>
        <p class="section-lede">
          报告本身负责稳定交付；Codex 更适合解释细节、改写成执行清单，或根据你的约束重新排优先级。
        </p>
      </div>
      <ul class="codex-list">
        {% for question in report.codex_questions %}
        <li>{{ question }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
